---
layout: base.njk
title: Festivals - Improvlore
permalink: /festivals/
pageDescription: Improv Lore has taken its shows on the road to improv festivals across Asia, from Singapore and Vietnam to Manila and Hong Kong.
---
{% from "cards.njk" import formatCard with context %}
{% from "badges.njk" import posterBadges %}

<div class="events-root">

  <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="section-fest-hero">
    <h1 class="section-heading" id="section-fest-hero">On the Road</h1>

    <div class="about-intro">
      <p class="about-lede">We are a Bangalore troupe, but the shows travel. Since 2024 we have been invited to improv festivals across Asia.</p>
      <p class="about-where">Singapore, Vietnam, Manila, Hong Kong. New cities, new crowds, troupes from all over on the same bill. We pack the formats we run at home and play them for a room that has never seen us.</p>
    </div>

    <ul class="about-stats" aria-label="Improv Lore festivals at a glance">
      <li>
        <span class="about-stat-num">4</span>
        <span class="about-stat-label">Festivals played</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="about-stat-num">4</span>
        <span class="about-stat-label">Cities abroad</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="about-stat-num">2024</span>
        <span class="about-stat-label">First trip out</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="section-fest-list">
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="section-fest-list">Where We've Played</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Invitations to festivals across the region, newest first.</p>

    <ol class="fest-timeline" aria-label="Festivals Improv Lore has played">
      {% for fest in festivals %}
      <li class="fest-stop">
        <span class="fest-stop-year">{{ fest.year }}</span>
        <div class="fest-stop-body">
          <strong>{{ fest.name }}</strong>
          <p><span class="fest-stop-city">{{ fest.city }}</span><span class="fest-stop-when">{{ fest.when }}</span></p>
        </div>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="section-fest-formats">
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="section-fest-formats">Formats We Take on the Road</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Two shows we built for the festival circuit, drawing on traditional Indian storytelling.</p>

    {# Pulled from the catalog by slug so the cards, posters, and /event/ pages
       never drift. Order here is the order shown. #}
    {% set roadSlugs = ["reincarnations", "panchatantra"] %}
    <ul class="about-shows" aria-label="Formats Improv Lore takes to festivals">
      {% for slug in roadSlugs %}
      {% for fmt in catalog %}{% if fmt.slug == slug %}{{ formatCard(fmt) }}{% endif %}{% endfor %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>

  {# The marathon: a hometown all-day event, kept short here so the touring
     story above stays the focus. A taste of the day (three of the eight slots),
     then out to marathon.improvlore.com for the rest and the next edition. The
     `marathonTaste` slugs pick which three; full lineup lives in marathon.js. #}
  <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="section-marathon">
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="section-marathon">A Festival at Home</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">We don't only play other people's festivals. On {{ marathon.meta.date }} we ran our first: <strong>{{ marathon.meta.name }}</strong>, {{ marathon.meta.tagline | lower }} of shows and jams back to back at {{ marathon.meta.venue }}.</p>

    {% set marathonTaste = ["the-great-face-off", "make-an-improv-song", "powerpoint-roulette"] %}
    <ul class="about-shows" aria-label="A taste of the marathon lineup">
      {% for slug in marathonTaste %}
      {% for slot in marathon.lineup %}{% if slot.slug == slug %}
      <li>
        <a class="about-show-card" href="/event/{{ slot.slug }}/">
          <div class="about-show-poster-wrap">
            <img class="about-show-poster" src="{{ slot.poster }}" alt="{{ slot.title }} poster" loading="lazy" sizes="(min-width: 960px) 360px, (min-width: 640px) 50vw, 100vw">
            {{ posterBadges([slot.type], slot.type) }}
          </div>
          <div class="about-show-body">
            <strong>{{ slot.title }}</strong>
            <span>{{ slot.blurb }}</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </li>
      {% endif %}{% endfor %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    <p class="more-line">
      That's {{ marathonTaste | length }} of {{ marathon.lineup | length }}. The full lineup, and word on when we do it again, lives at
      <a href="{{ marathon.meta.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">marathon.improvlore.com →</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section page-section-info" aria-labelledby="section-fest-more">
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="section-fest-more">Catch Us Closer to Home</h2>

    <a class="corporate-banner" href="/events/">
      <span class="corporate-banner-text">
        <strong>Most weeks you'll find us in Bangalore.</strong>
        Weekly jams, workshops, and shows at Underline Center and around the city.
      </span>
      <span class="corporate-banner-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
  </section>

</div>
